<!-- Process -->
<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <span class="section-label">Our Approach</span>
      <h2>The Pre-Construction Process</h2>

      <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 2rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-accent);">1. Initial Consultation</h3>
          <p>We meet with your team to understand your vision, goals, timeline, and budget parameters. This discovery phase allows us to align our approach with your specific needs.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 2rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-accent);">2. Design Review & Analysis</h3>
          <p>Our experienced team reviews architectural plans and specifications, providing constructability input and identifying potential issues before they become expensive problems.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 2rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-accent);">3. Value Engineering</h3>
          <p>We analyze the design for opportunities to optimize costs through alternative materials, methods, or approaches—always maintaining quality and meeting your functional requirements.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 2rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-accent);">4. Budget Development</h3>
          <p>Detailed cost estimates broken down by system and trade, giving you transparency and control. We provide multiple scenarios when applicable so you can make informed decisions.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 2rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-accent);">5. Schedule Planning</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive project timelines accounting for design completion, permitting, procurement lead times, and construction phases. We build in realistic contingencies and coordination points.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="padding-left: 2rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-accent);">6. Final Proposal</h3>
          <p>A complete pre-construction package including refined budgets, schedules, value engineering recommendations, and a clear path forward to construction. You'll have everything needed to make confident decisions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

